These poky staff areas vary in style. Some more luxurious offerings offer airline employees pjyamas and entertainment systems. 

The rest areas are often hidden in a compartment at the top of the plane, or a sealed off section in the same main cabin as the regular passengers.

On a Cathay Pacific 777-300ER a secret staircase to the CRC at the rear of the plane. The area itself is tunnel like, and attendants have to duck to get through it, but there is room for eight flight staff. 

 

